 pain, dark urine, pale stools, and jaundice.', 'Synergism', 'Caution is advised if lomitapide is used with other potentially hepatotoxic agents (e.', 'Major', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/269975/', '', 'Cholestyramine, Rosuvastatin, Fenofibrate, Evinacumab, Dextrothyroxine, Simvastatin, Probucol, Cerivastatin, Ezetimibe, Niacin, Atorvastatin, More', 'Amphetamine, Metamfetamine, Lisdexamfetamine, Solriamfetol, Caffeine, Methylphenidate, Dexmethylphenidate, Dextroamphetamine, Citicoline', 1767369485);
